<bibRefCitation id="7D514B5AFF99FFF8A04BBAC4FB5AF3E6" author="Buining, A. F. H. &amp; Brederoo, A. J." box="[800,1167,446,473]" pageId="7" pageNumber="160" refId="ref8048" refString="Buining, A. F. H. &amp; Brederoo, A. J. (1973) Frailea lepida Buining et Brederoo spec. nov. Kakteen 54: CVIe." type="book" year="1973">Buining &amp; Brederoo (1973: 106)</bibRefCitation>
